   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>When visiting <a href="http://openhatch.org/account/signup/">http://openhatch.org/account/signup/</a> in Chromium, it looks great.

When visiting the same link in Firefox (or in my case, Iceweasel), the alignment
looks off.

Pam, I'm tentatively assigning this to you in the hopes you might be able to
take a look. Feel free to de-assign if you can't!

(Also, feel very free to poke around the site looking for other CSS-y oddities
in Firefox.)</pre>
